Suggested layout for your PRG:<br />16 KB bank 0: bankswitched stuff.<br />16 KB bank 1: bankswitched stuff.<br />16 KB bank 2: instructions on how to build an atomic bomb.<br />16 KB bank 3: hardwired stuff.<br /><br />Just stick a random text file in there as an easter egg; that's what was done for The New Tetris on N64.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Wed Apr 06, 2005 7:38 pm</p><hr />
